Right, right, okay. I think you're right.

934
01:00:24,720 --> 01:00:27,190
或者我们可以把它交给某个
Or we could give it to somebody

935
01:00:27,190 --> 01:00:28,640
不会逮捕我们的
who's not going to arrest us,

936
01:00:28,800 --> 01:00:30,040
大好人
who's really nice

937
01:00:30,200 --> 01:00:31,880
然后大赚一笔
for a whole lot of money.

938
01:00:32,040 --> 01:00:32,970
我觉得这是个
I think it's a really good

939
01:00:32,970 --> 01:00:34,560
能两全其美的好方法
balance between both of your points of view.

940
01:00:34,720 --> 01:00:35,720
你太卑鄙
You're despicable.

941
01:00:36,400 --> 01:00:37,400
太无耻
Dishonorable.

942
01:00:38,040 --> 01:00:39,040
毫无信用
Faithless!

943
01:00:39,760 --> 01:00:41,330
-不  -终于
- No. - At last!

944
01:00:43,840 --> 01:00:46,360
我要面对我的仇敌并且亲手解决他了
I shall meet my foe and destroy him.

945
01:00:46,520 --> 01:00:48,240
是你叫来了罗南
You called Ronan?

946
01:00:53,080 --> 01:00:56,120
奎尔  别想跑  小子
Quill! Don't you move, boy!

947
