Ronan the Accuser!

949
01:01:05,840 --> 01:01:08,570
是你传送的信息吗
You are the one who transmitted the message?

950
01:01:08,570 --> 01:01:09,770
你杀了我妻子
You killed my wife.

951
01:01:10,720 --> 01:01:12,520
你杀了我女儿
You killed my daughter!

952
01:01:20,000 --> 01:01:21,760
我都说了  你进不来的
I told you, you can't fit.

953
01:01:21,760 --> 01:01:23,800
在这儿等我回来
Now, wait here. I'll be back.

954
01:01:29,440 --> 01:01:32,760
是卡魔拉  她带着宇宙灵球逃走了
It is Gamora. She is escaping with the Orb.

955
01:01:41,560 --> 01:01:43,210
不
No!

956
01:01:43,320 --> 01:01:44,320
星云
Nebula,

957
01:01:45,160 --> 01:01:46,810
去夺回宇宙灵球
retrieve the Orb.

958
01:02:03,320 --> 01:02:05,240
宝石在最前面那个作业舱里
The Stone is in the furthest pod.

959
01:02:05,920 --> 01:02:07,200
击落它
Bring it down!

960
01:02:35,800 --> 01:02:38,920
火箭  掩护卡魔拉到米拉诺号
Rocket, keep them off Gamora until she gets to the Milano.

961
01:02:39,080 --> 01:02:41,480
怎么掩护  这上面又没有武器
How? We've got no weaponry on these things.

962
01:02:41,640 --> 01:02:43,500
这些作业舱都是工业级的
These pods are industrial grade.

963
01:02:43,500 --> 01:02:45,120
基本上坚不可摧
They're nearly indestructible.

964
01:02:45,120 --> 01:02:47,390
那也吃不消死灵炮啊
Not against necroblasts, they're not.

965
01:02:47,560 --> 01:02:49,160
我可不是那个意思
That's not what I'm saying.

966
01:03:37,640 --> 01:03:39,320
借你飞船用一用
Let me borrow your ride.

967
01:04:12,080 --> 01:04:13,920
我不记得杀过你家人
I don't recall killing your family.

968
01:04:17,240 --> 01:04:20,600
大概也不会记得杀过你
I doubt I'll remember killing you, either.

969
01:04:37,240 --> 01:04:40,080
奎尔  我被困住了  到不了米拉诺号
Quill, I'm trapped. I can't make it to the Milano.

970
01:04:40,720 --> 01:04:41,960
