罗南  东西到手了
Ronan, it is done.

980
01:06:09,760 --> 01:06:10,800
奎尔  算了
Quill, come on.

981
01:06:11,400 --> 01:06:13,840
她的身体改造过  大概能撑几分钟
Her body mods should keep her alive a couple more minutes,

982
