but there's nothing we can do for her.

983
01:06:16,200 --> 01:06:17,720
这些作业舱在外面坚持不了多久的
These pods aren't meant to be out here.

984
01:06:17,840 --> 01:06:20,240
很快  我们也会像她一样
In a second, we're gonna be in the same boat.

985
01:06:27,760 --> 01:06:30,080
去他的
Aw, damn it.

986
01:06:31,400 --> 01:06:32,840
奎尔
Quill?

987
