勇度  勇度
Yondu! Yondu.

988
01:06:35,120 --> 01:06:36,210
我是奎尔
This is Quill!

989
01:06:36,240 --> 01:06:39,800
-我现在的坐标是227K324  -奎尔
- My coordinates are 227K324. - Quill.

990
01:06:40,040 --> 01:06:41,200
奎尔  你在干什么
Quill, what are you doing?

991
01:06:41,360 --> 01:06:42,810
就在无存知地外面
Just outside Knowhere.

992
01:06:42,960 --> 01:06:45,080
如果你在的话  就来抓我吧
If you're there, come get me.

993
01:06:45,800 --> 01:06:47,290
我随你处置
I'm all yours.

994
01:06:56,760 --> 01:06:58,720
奎尔  别犯傻
Quill, don't be ridiculous.

995
01:07:00,320 --> 01:07:02,440
回你的作业舱里去
Get back into your pod!

996
01:07:02,800 --> 01:07:05,880
里面装不下两个人  你会死的
You can't fit two people in there. You're gonna die.

997
01:07:07,120 --> 01:07:08,960
你马上就会死的
You'll die in seconds!

998
01:07:09,280 --> 01:07:10,440
奎尔
Quill.

999
01:08:11,520 --> 01:08:13,170
奎尔
Quill?

1000
01:08:14,840 --> 01:08:16,330
怎么了
What happened?

1001
01:08:17,480 --> 01:08:19,520
我看见你漂浮在外面
I saw you out there.

1002
01:08:20,920 --> 01:08:23,400
我也不知道自己怎么了
I don't know what came over me.

1003
01:08:24,360 --> 01:08:26,200
我不能眼睁睁让你死
But I couldn't let you die.

1004
01:08:29,040 --> 01:08:31,440
我突然感受到了内心深处的一种
I found something inside of myself.

1005
01:08:32,480 --> 01:08:34,050
一种
Something

1006
01:08:34,200 --> 01:08:36,980
难以置信的英雄气概
incredibly heroic.

1007
01:08:37,920 --> 01:08:40,440
我不是在夸自己
I mean, not to brag,

1008
01:08:40,600 --> 01:08:41,920
可是  客观地说
but, objectively...

1009
01:08:42,000 --> 01:08:43,040
宇宙灵球呢
Where's the Orb?

1010
