他们把宇宙灵球抢走了
It's... Well, they got the Orb.

1011
01:08:47,280 --> 01:08:48,320
什么
What?

1012
01:08:51,040 --> 01:08:53,520
欢迎回家  彼得
Welcome home, Peter.

1013
01:09:16,400 --> 01:09:19,160
蠢货  全是无可救药的蠢货
Blasted idiot. They're all idiots!

1014
01:09:20,480 --> 01:09:22,760
奎尔竟然自投罗网了
Quill just got himself captured.

1015
01:09:22,920 --> 01:09:24,560
要不是你
None of this ever would have

1016
01:09:24,560 --> 01:09:27,200
一意孤行  非要去单挑罗南
happened if you didn't try to single-handedly

1017
01:09:27,360 --> 01:09:28,600
这一切都不会发生
take on a frickin' army!

1018
