"我的老婆孩子都死了"
Boo-hoo-hoo. "My wife and child are dead."

1024
01:10:01,000 --> 01:10:03,200
我才不在乎这有多残忍
I don't care if it's mean!

1025
01:10:03,360 --> 01:10:05,240
谁家没死过人
Everybody's got dead people.

1026
01:10:05,920 --> 01:10:07,570
不代表你就有理由让大家
It's no excuse to get everybody else

1027
01:10:07,760 --> 01:10:09,640
陪你一起送死
dead along the way!

1028
01:10:13,440 --> 01:10:16,120
好了  格鲁特  罗南拿到了宝石
Come on, Groot. Ronan has the Stone.

1029
01:10:16,280 --> 01:10:17,400
我们现在唯一能做的
The only chance we got

1030
01:10:17,400 --> 01:10:19,610
就是赶紧飞往宇宙另一头去
is to get to the other side of the universe

1031
01:10:19,640 --> 01:10:21,520
越快越好
as fast as we can and maybe,

1032
01:10:21,680 --> 01:10:24,300
也许趁着那神经病还没打过来
just maybe, we'll be able to live full lives

1033
01:10:24,300 --> 01:10:26,320
能安稳的过一辈子
before that whack-job ever gets there.

1034
01:10:28,800 --> 01:10:30,160
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1035
01:10:30,320 --> 01:10:32,600
救他们  怎么救
Save them? How?

1036
01:10:32,760 --> 01:10:35,520
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1037
01:10:35,680 --> 01:10:38,420
我知道他们是我们唯一的朋友
I know they're the only friends that we ever had,

1038
01:10:38,420 --> 01:10:41,170
可他们现在落在掠夺者军队手里
but there's an army of Ravagers around them.

1039
01:10:41,320 --> 01:10:42,970
我们只有两个人
And there's only two of us!

1040
01:10:44,000 --> 01:10:45,240
是三个
Three.

1041
01:10:54,320 --> 01:10:56,560
我都被你们气得
You're making me

1042
01:10:56,720 --> 01:10:58,290
只能  拿草
beat...up

1043
01:10:58,480 --> 01:10:59,480
撒气了
grass!

1044
01:11:02,000 --> 01:11:03,720
宇宙灵球已经在我手里了
The Orb is in my possession,

1045
01:11:04,840 --> 01:11:06,360
我说到做到
as I promised.

1046
01:11:06,520 --> 01:11:08,040
把它送到我这里来
Bring it to me.

1047
01:11:08,240 --> 01:11:11,520
没错  这是我们之前约定好的
Yes, that was our agreement.

1048
01:11:12,280 --> 01:11:13,930
我帮你拿来宇宙灵球
Bring you the Orb,

1049
01:11:14,120 --> 01:11:17,640
你帮我毁灭山达尔
and you will destroy Xandar for me.

1050
01:11:17,800 --> 01:11:22,360
不过  既然我知道了它装有无限宝石
However, now that I know it contains an Infinity Stone,

1051
01:11:22,520 --> 01:11:24,520
我很好奇我还要你做什么
I wonder what use I have for you.

1052
01:11:24,680 --> 01:11:26,200
小子
Boy,

1053
01:11:26,520 --> 01:11:29,110
你最好给我想清楚了
I would reconsider your current course.

1054
01:11:30,120 --> 01:11:32,360
主人  你不能这么做
Master! You cannot!

1055
01:11:32,520 --> 01:11:35,040
灭霸是这宇宙中最强大的存在
Thanos is the most powerful being in the universe.

1056
01:11:35,680 --> 01:11:37,330
不再是了
Not anymore.

1057
01:12:00,160 --> 01:12:02,400
你竟然叫我"小子"
You call me "Boy!"

1058
01:12:02,560 --> 01:12:03,800
我会代表克里
I will unfurl

1059
01:12:03,800 --> 01:12:07,120
对千年来山达尔的所作所为进行审判
1,000 years of Kree justice on Xandar,

1060
01:12:07,280 --> 01:12:10,800
让它消失殆尽
and burn it to its core!

1061
01:12:10,960 --> 01:12:12,920
之后  灭霸
Then, Thanos,

1062
01:12:13,080 --> 01:12:15,040
我就去找你算账
I am coming for you.

1063
01:12:17,400 --> 01:12:20,320
毁灭山达尔之后  你会杀掉我父亲吗
After Xandar, you are going to kill my father?

1064
01:12:20,800 --> 01:12:22,640
你想反抗我吗
You dare to oppose me?

1065
01:12:22,800 --> 01:12:24,690
你也看到他对我做了些什么
You see what he has turned me into.

1066
01:12:24,720 --> 01:12:28,960
你杀了他  我会再帮你毁灭一千个星球
If you kill him, I will help you destroy a thousand planets.

1067
01:12:29,760 --> 01:12:31,280
你敢背叛我?
You betray me?

1068
01:12:32,200 --> 01:12:33,200
偷我的钱?
Steal my money?

1069
01:12:33,320 --> 01:12:34,920
住手  放开他
Stop it! Leave him alone!

1070
01:12:35,320 --> 01:12:37,400
你小时候刚被我捡到的时候
When I picked you up as a kid,

1071
01:12:37,560 --> 01:12:39,880
这些小子想吃了你
these boys wanted to eat you.

1072
01:12:40,080 --> 01:12:42,480
他们还没尝过地星人的味道呢
They ain't never tasted Terran before.

1073
01:12:42,640 --> 01:12:44,410
是我救了你
I saved your life!

1074
01:12:44,440 --> 01:12:46,590
还有完没完啊  天哪
Will you shut up about that? God!

1075
01:12:46,760 --> 01:12:49,130
二十年了  一直给我说这些陈芝麻烂谷子
Twenty years, you been throwing that in my face,

1076
01:12:49,160 --> 01:12:51,930
好像没有吃掉我是件多么伟大的事
like it's some great thing, not eating me.

1077
01:12:51,960 --> 01:12:55,520
正常人哪会每天想着吃人啊
Normal people don't even think about eating someone else!

1078
01:12:55,720 --> 01:12:58,160
不吃我难道我还得谢你吗
Much less that person having to be grateful for it!

1079
01:12:58,320 --> 01:12:59,960
是你劫持了我
You abducted me, man.

1080
01:13:00,480 --> 01:13:02,720
把我从家里掳走  害我无亲无故
You stole me from my home and from my family.

1081
01:13:02,880 --> 01:13:05,000
你他妈才不是因为在乎你们地星
You don't give a damn about your Terra!

1082
01:13:05,520 --> 01:13:06,520
你害怕
You're scared

1083
01:13:06,680 --> 01:13:08,850
不过是因为内心太懦弱了
because you're soft in here.

1084
01:13:08,880 --> 01:13:09,960
这里  就在这里
Here, right here!

1085
01:13:10,320 --> 01:13:11,320
勇度
Yondu!

1086
01:13:11,480 --> 01:13:12,770
听我说
Listen to me.

1087
01:13:12,800 --> 01:13:15,040
罗南掌握着一块叫无限宝石的东西
Ronan has something called an Infinity Stone.

1088
01:13:15,160 --> 01:13:16,960
我知道他手里有什么  小姑娘
I know what he's got, girl.

1089
