他会用宝石摧毁掉山达尔
He's gonna use it to wipe out Xandar.

1091
01:13:23,160 --> 01:13:24,550
我们得警告他们
We have to warn them.

1092
01:13:24,550 --> 01:13:26,250
否则无数的人会因此丧命
Billions of people will perish.

1093
01:13:26,280 --> 01:13:28,970
她就是这样给你洗脑的吗  小子
Is that what she's been filling your head with, boy?

1094
01:13:29,000 --> 01:13:30,120
多愁善感
Sentiment?

1095
01:13:31,480 --> 01:13:33,490
蛆虫一样蚕食掉你的大脑
Eating away your brain like maggots!

1096
01:13:38,080 --> 01:13:39,490
就这样吧
That's it.

1097
01:13:40,160 --> 01:13:41,200
不
No!

1098
01:13:41,680 --> 01:13:42,760
抱歉了  小子
Sorry, boy.

1099
01:13:42,920 --> 01:13:44,710
身为队长  必须杀一儆百
But a captain's gotta teach his men

1100
01:13:44,710 --> 01:13:46,440
让手下知道背叛会是什么下场
what happens to those what cross him.

1101
01:13:46,600 --> 01:13:48,200
队长要以身作则
Captain's gotta teach stuff!

1102
01:13:50,680 --> 01:13:52,920
如果你现在杀了我
If you kill me now,

1103
01:13:53,080 --> 01:13:57,210
就别想做成这辈子最大一笔生意了
you are saying goodbye to the biggest score you have ever seen.

1104
01:14:02,360 --> 01:14:03,770
无限宝石吗
The Stone?

1105
01:14:04,520 --> 01:14:06,480
你最好能想出个别的
I hope you got something better than that.

1106
01:14:06,640 --> 01:14:09,290
没有人能从罗南手里偷东西
Because ain't nobody stealing from Ronan.

1107
