his army.

1112
01:14:20,160 --> 01:14:22,000
他也有弱点
He's vulnerable.

1113
01:14:22,800 --> 01:14:24,170
你觉得怎么样  勇度
Hey, what do you say, Yondu?

1114
01:14:24,200 --> 01:14:27,760
我和你  还跟以前一样  携手作战
Me and you, taking down a mark side-by-side, like the old days.

1115
01:14:35,480 --> 01:14:36,560
放开他
Let him go!

1116
01:14:38,280 --> 01:14:40,800
你小子一向有种
You always did have a scrote, boy!

1117
01:14:40,960 --> 01:14:43,730
所以我当时才留你在身边
That's why I kept you on as a young'un.

1118
01:14:52,000 --> 01:14:53,960
队长  这种攻击不痛不痒的
Captain, the shot was non-damaging.

1119
01:14:54,120 --> 01:14:56,320
请注意  蠢货们
Attention, idiots.

1120
01:14:58,400 --> 01:15:02,200
飞船上这个疯子手里拿着的是强子枪
The lunatic on top of this craft is holding a Hadron Enforcer.

1121
01:15:02,360 --> 01:15:04,080
我独家设计的武器
It's a weapon of my own design.

1122
01:15:04,240 --> 01:15:05,360
这是在搞什么
What the hell?

1123
01:15:05,840 --> 01:15:08,520
要是你们不赶紧交出我朋友
If you don't hand over our companions now,

1124
01:15:08,720 --> 01:15:11,000
他就把你们的飞船轰出个新鲜的洞
he's gonna tear your ship a new one.

1125
01:15:11,160 --> 01:15:12,920
又大又新鲜的洞
A very big new one!

1126
01:15:13,080 --> 01:15:15,920
-老子才不买你的账  -我倒数五下
- I ain't buyin' it. - I'm giving you to the count of five.

1127
01:15:16,480 --> 01:15:19,600
-5  4  3  -别  等一下
- 5, 4, 3... - No! Wait, hold on!

1128
01:15:19,760 --> 01:15:21,520
火箭  是我  真是的
Rocket, it's me, for God sakes!

1129
01:15:21,680 --> 01:15:23,680
已经谈拢了  我们没事了
We figured it out! We're fine!

1130
01:15:23,840 --> 01:15:25,400
奎尔  怎么回事
Hey, Quill. What's going on?

1131
01:15:26,920 --> 01:15:28,650
这就叫"谈拢了"
You call that "Figured it out"?

1132
01:15:28,680 --> 01:15:29,830
要从那群把我们
We're gonna rob the guys

1133
01:15:29,830 --> 01:15:31,240
打得屁滚尿流的家伙手里抢东西
who just beat us senseless.

1134
01:15:31,240 --> 01:15:32,650
你还有脸说屁滚尿流
You want to talk about senseless?

1135
01:15:32,680 --> 01:15:35,050
你到底是想救我们还是想把我们炸飞
How about trying to save us by blowing us up?

1136
01:15:35,080 --> 01:15:36,750
他们要是不交出你们
We were only gonna blow you up

1137
01:15:36,750 --> 01:15:37,970
我才会把他们炸飞
if they didn't turn you over!

1138
01:15:38,000 --> 01:15:39,800
你只数五下
And how on earth were they gonna turn us over

1139
01:15:39,960 --> 01:15:41,520
他们哪有时间交出我们
when you only gave them a count of five?

1140
01:15:41,640 --> 01:15:43,960
我们又没空考虑倒数时间
We didn't have time to work out the minutiae

1141
01:15:44,120 --> 01:15:45,170
那些细节
of the plan.

1142
01:15:45,200 --> 01:15:47,570
我们为朋友两肋插刀就这下场
This is what we get for acting altruistically.

1143
01:15:47,600 --> 01:15:49,680
-我是格鲁特  -他们根本不领情
- I am Groot. - They are ungrateful.

1144
01:15:49,840 --> 01:15:50,960
重点是
What's important now

1145
01:15:51,120 --> 01:15:52,770
我们说服了掠夺者军队
is we get the Ravagers' army

1146
01:15:52,920 --> 01:15:54,170
帮我们拯救山达尔
to help us save Xandar.

1147
01:15:54,200 --> 01:15:55,730
然后我们再把宝石交给勇度
So we can give the Stone to Yondu

1148
01:15:55,760 --> 01:15:57,780
好让他卖给一个更邪恶的家伙吗
who's just gonna sell to somebody even worse?

1149
01:15:57,780 --> 01:15:59,200
这个之后再议
We'll figure that part out later.

1150
01:15:59,280 --> 01:16:01,010
我们必须阻止罗南
We have to stop Ronan.

1151
01:16:01,040 --> 01:16:02,480
怎么阻止
How?

1152
01:16:02,640 --> 01:16:03,770
我有个计划
I have a plan.

1153
01:16:03,800 --> 01:16:04,800
你有个计划?
You've got a plan?

1154
01:16:05,320 --> 01:16:06,320
没错
Yes.

1155
01:16:06,840 --> 01:16:07,920
首先  那句话是我说的
First of all, you're copying me from

1156
01:16:08,040 --> 01:16:09,450
-你算是抄袭  -哪有
- when I said I had a plan. - No, I'm not.

1157
01:16:09,600 --> 01:16:10,860
这话谁都会说
People say that all the time.

1158
01:16:10,860 --> 01:16:12,570
又没什么特别的
It's not that unique of a thing to say.

1159
01:16:12,600 --> 01:16:14,440
其次  我不相信你有什么计划
Secondly, I don't even believe you have a plan.

1160
01:16:14,600 --> 01:16:17,330
我有一部分计划
I have part of a plan!

1161
01:16:17,480 --> 01:16:19,000
一部分是多少
What percentage of a plan do you have?

1162
01:16:19,160 --> 01:16:20,570
鉴于你在无存知地的表现
You don't get to ask questions

1163
01:16:20,680 --> 01:16:22,320
你没有权利提问
after the nonsense you pulled on Knowhere.

1164
01:16:22,440 --> 01:16:24,130
我可救了奎尔
I just saved Quill.

1165
01:16:24,160 --> 01:16:25,210
我们已经讨论过了
We've already established

1166
01:16:25,240 --> 01:16:27,080
你们想炸了我乘坐的飞船  那可不是在救我
that you destroying the ship that I'm on is not saving me.

1167
01:16:27,080 --> 01:16:28,130
我们什么时候讨论过了
When did we establish it?

1168
01:16:28,130 --> 01:16:29,160
就几秒钟以前
Like three seconds ago!

1169
01:16:29,320 --> 01:16:31,400
我没在仔细听  那会儿正走神
I wasn't listening. I was thinking of something else.

1170
01:16:32,000 --> 01:16:33,520
她说得没错  你没有发表意见的权利
She's right. You don't get an opinion.

1171
01:16:33,920 --> 01:16:35,000
你有百分之多少的计划
What percentage?

1172
01:16:35,160 --> 01:16:36,570
我不知道  百分之十二吧
I don't know. Twelve percent.

1173
01:16:36,600 --> 01:16:38,010
百分之十二?
Twelve percent?

1174
01:16:39,960 --> 01:16:41,080
你笑得真假
That's a fake laugh.

1175
01:16:41,280 --> 01:16:43,050
-是真的  -太假了
- It's real! - Totally fake.

1176
01:16:43,080 --> 01:16:45,340
这是我这辈子笑得最真实
That is the most real, authentic,

1177
01:16:45,350 --> 01:16:47,680
最歇斯底里的一次了
hysterical laugh of my entire life

1178
01:16:47,840 --> 01:16:49,190
因为你这是狗屁计划
because that is not a plan.

1179
01:16:49,190 --> 01:16:50,450
只能算是一个想法
It's barely a concept.

1180
01:16:50,600 --> 01:16:51,600
你站到他们那一边去了吗
You're taking their side?

1181
01:16:51,760 --> 01:16:52,960
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1182
01:16:53,120 --> 01:16:54,530
是比百分之十一要强点  又怎样
So what, it's better than 11%?

1183
01:16:54,560 --> 01:16:56,130
你那狗屁计划能有什么用
What the hell does that have to do with anything?

1184
01:16:56,160 --> 01:16:58,360
谢谢你  格鲁特  谢谢
Thank you, Groot. Thank you.

1185
01:16:58,880 --> 01:17:02,320
格鲁特是你们当中唯一一个明事理的
See? Groot's the only one of you who has a clue.

1186
01:17:07,360 --> 01:17:08,360
伙伴们
Guys.

1187
01:17:09,200 --> 01:17:10,280
拜托
Come on.

1188
01:17:10,440 --> 01:17:12,530
勇度马上就要过来了
Yondu is gonna be here in two seconds.

1189
01:17:12,560 --> 01:17:15,040
他还想听听我们的大计划呢
He expects to hear this big plan of ours.

1190
01:17:16,440 --> 01:17:18,360
我需要你们的帮助
I need your help.

1191
01:17:20,040 --> 01:17:22,400
看看我们
I look around at us.

1192
01:17:22,880 --> 01:17:23,920
知道我看到了什么吗
You know what I see?

1193
01:17:24,880 --> 01:17:26,320
一群失败者
Losers.

1194
01:17:28,560 --> 01:17:30,130
我们就像
I mean, like,

1195
01:17:30,280 --> 01:17:32,290
一群失魂落魄的家伙
folks who have lost stuff.

1196
01:17:32,320 --> 01:17:34,480
确实如此  我们所有人都失去过
And we have. Man, we have. All of us.

1197
01:17:35,600 --> 01:17:36,930
失去了家
Our homes,

1198
01:17:37,640 --> 01:17:39,050
失去了家人
our families,

1199
01:17:40,160 --> 01:17:42,080
失去了正常的生活
normal lives.

1200
01:17:42,240 --> 01:17:43,980
没错  生活本来就是付出比回报更多
And, usually, life takes more than it gives.

1201
01:17:43,980 --> 01:17:45,210
可今天不是
But not today.

1202
01:17:45,800 --> 01:17:47,320
今天我们得到了眷顾
Today, it's given us something.

1203
01:17:47,480 --> 01:17:49,050
生活给了我们一个机会
It has given us a chance.

1204
01:17:49,200 --> 01:17:50,560
什么机会
To do what?

1205
01:17:52,400 --> 01:17:53,760
去拼一回
To give a shit.

1206
01:17:54,520 --> 01:17:56,320
仅此一回
For once.

1207
01:17:56,520 --> 01:17:58,520
不要逃避
Not run away.

1208
01:18:01,360 --> 01:18:03,890
罗南要屠杀无数无辜的生命
I, for one, am not gonna stand by and watch

1209
01:18:03,920 --> 01:18:07,000
而我  绝不会袖手旁观
as Ronan wipes out billions of innocent lives.

1210
01:18:08,120 --> 01:18:10,720
可是  奎尔  想要阻止罗南
But, Quill, stopping Ronan,

1211
01:18:11,800 --> 01:18:13,840
是不可能的
it's impossible.

1212
01:18:14,360 --> 01:18:16,640
你是在叫我们去送死
You're asking us to die.

1213
01:18:23,320 --> 01:18:25,200
是啊  应该是吧
Yeah, I guess I am.

1214
01:18:38,040 --> 01:18:39,160
奎尔
Quill.

1215
01:18:43,360 --> 01:18:46,680
我活了这么久  只跟敌人打过交道
I have lived most my life surrounded by my enemies.

1216
01:18:50,720 --> 01:18:54,930
我愿意和朋友共生死
I will be grateful to die among my friends.

1217
01:18:59,240 --> 01:19:01,380
你是个有担当的男人  奎尔
You are an honorable man, Quill.

1218
01:19:02,880 --> 01:19:05,080
我愿意跟你并肩作战
I will fight beside you.

1219
01:19:06,280 --> 01:19:07,800
最后
And in the end,

1220
01:19:09,760 --> 01:19:11,800
我就能和我的妻女团聚了
I will see my wife and daughter again.

1221
01:19:17,760 --> 01:19:20,920
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1222
01:19:31,240 --> 01:19:34,480
随你们吧  反正本来我也活不长
What the hell. I don't got that long a lifespan, anyway.

1223
01:19:40,480 --> 01:19:42,720
我也站起来了  你们满意了吧
Now I'm standing. Y'all happy?

1224
01:19:43,200 --> 01:19:45,360
现在我们都站起来了
We're all standing up now.

1225
01:19:45,520 --> 01:19:48,850
一群傻缺  站成个圈圈
Bunch of jackasses, standing in a circle.

1226
01:19:56,040 --> 01:19:57,560
宝石会对任何有机体产生反应
The Stone reacts to anything organic.

1227
01:19:57,720 --> 01:19:59,810
目标越大  威力越强
The bigger the target, the bigger the power surge.

1228
01:19:59,840 --> 01:20:00,890
罗南只需要让宝石
All Ronan's got to do is

1229
01:20:00,890 --> 01:20:03,000
接触到星球的表面  它就会毁掉一切
touch the Stone to the planet's surface and zap.

1230
01:20:03,160 --> 01:20:04,810
所有的植物  动物
All plants, animals,

1231
01:20:04,960 --> 01:20:06,720
-新星军团  -一切都将被毁灭
- Nova Corps. - Everything will die.

1232
01:20:07,080 --> 01:20:09,040
所以不能让罗南登陆
So Ronan does not make the surface.

1233
01:20:12,000 --> 01:20:13,960
火箭带领一队人马在暗黑星号右舷
Rocket will lead a team to blow a hole

1234
01:20:14,160 --> 01:20:16,280
轰开一个洞
in the Dark Aster's starboard hull.

1235
01:20:16,440 --> 01:20:20,570
这样我们和勇度的飞船就可以攻进去了
Then, our craft and Yondu's will enter.

1236
01:20:20,600 --> 01:20:23,450
里面有上百个萨卡士兵把守吧
Won't there be hundreds of Sakaaran soldiers inside?

1237
01:20:23,480 --> 01:20:26,320
萨卡士兵都是纸做的
I think of Sakaaran as paper people.

1238
01:20:32,440 --> 01:20:33,640
他们一旦得知我们登陆了
Once they know we're on board,

1239
01:20:33,720 --> 01:20:35,020
罗南会关上舱内的安全门
Ronan will isolate himself

1240
01:20:35,020 --> 01:20:37,170
把自己隔离起来
behind impenetrable security doors on deck.

1241
01:20:37,200 --> 01:20:39,640
我可以通过破坏动力系统解锁
Which I can disable by dismantling the power source.

1242
01:20:39,800 --> 01:20:41,570
接着我们进到驾驶舱
We'll make it to the flight deck,

1243
01:20:41,600 --> 01:20:45,020
用强子枪把罗南轰上天
and I'll use the Hadron Enforcer to kill Ronan.

1244
01:20:46,800 --> 01:20:50,240
罗南一死我们就回收宝石
Once Ronan is dead, we will retrieve the Stone.

1245
01:20:50,760 --> 01:20:53,280
记得要把它装进这些装置里
Use these devices to contain it.

1246
01:20:53,490 --> 01:20:54,990
别直接触摸
If you touch it,

1247
01:20:55,360 --> 01:20:56,620
不然小命就没了
it will kill you.

1248
01:20:59,520 --> 01:21:02,620
我会联络之前逮捕过我们的新星警官
I'll contact one of the Nova officers who arrested us.

1249
01:21:02,920 --> 01:21:04,780
但愿他们相信我们是来帮忙的
Hopefully, they'll believe we're there to help.

1250
01:21:03,870 --> 01:21:05,670
{\an8}正在呼入

1251
01:21:03,870 --> 01:21:05,670
{\an8}彼得·奎尔

1252
01:21:06,080 --> 01:21:09,240
完成计划还需要最后一步
There's one more thing we need to complete the plan.

1253
01:21:10,000 --> 01:21:11,200
那家伙的眼睛
That guy's eye.

1254
01:21:12,120 --> 01:21:13,590
不  瞎说什么呢
No! No, we don't.

1255
01:21:13,630 --> 01:21:16,130
我们不需要那家伙的眼睛
No, we don't need that guy's eye.

1256
01:21:16,700 --> 01:21:19,840
不  说真的  对我来说相当重要呢
No, seriously, I need it! It's important to me.

1257
01:21:24,520 --> 01:21:26,250
已发现罗南舰队
Ronan's fleet has been spotted,

1258
01:21:26,280 --> 01:21:29,280
预计十五分钟后抵达
and will arrive in T-minus fifteen minutes.

1259
01:21:29,560 --> 01:21:31,050
听好了  小子
Remember, boy.

1260
01:21:31,480 --> 01:21:33,360
这事完了之后
At the end of all this,

1261
01:21:33,520 --> 01:21:34,950
宝石归我
I get the Stone.

1262
01:21:35,030 --> 01:21:37,780
敢耍我就砍死你们
You cross me, we kill you all.

1263
01:21:59,600 --> 01:22:01,370
准备大干一场吧  小子们
Let's go get 'em, boys!

1264
01:22:10,880 --> 01:22:11,940
这计划烂死了
This is a terrible plan.

1265
01:22:11,970 --> 01:22:14,720
不是你说要和朋友共生死的吗
Hey, you're the one who said you wanted to die among friends.

1266
01:22:20,000 --> 01:22:20,990
新星至尊
Nova Prime.

1267
01:22:22,160 --> 01:22:24,620
一个掠夺者刚刚给我传达了一则消息
I received a transmission from one of the Ravagers.

1268
01:22:24,700 --> 01:22:27,880
他说罗南得到了一颗什么无限宝石
He says Ronan's in possession of something called an Infinity Stone

1269
01:22:27,960 --> 01:22:29,370
正冲着山达尔来
and he's headed toward Xandar.

1270
01:22:29,400 --> 01:22:30,250
老天爷
Good God.

1271
01:22:30,400 --> 01:22:32,680
不过是个幌子  别忘了他是罪犯
It's a trick. He's a criminal.

1272
01:22:32,880 --> 01:22:35,170
他有说我们为什么要相信他吗
Did he say why we should believe him?

1273
01:22:35,400 --> 01:22:37,560
他说他们一帮人刚刚越狱
He said his crew just escaped from prison,

1274
01:22:37,760 --> 01:22:40,730
如果不是为了拯救山达尔没理由冒险
so he'd have no other reason to risk coming to Xandar to help.

1275
01:22:41,560 --> 01:22:43,140
他说他确实是个
He says that he's an...

1276
01:22:43,760 --> 01:22:44,980
"混球"
"A-hole."

1277
01:22:45,160 --> 01:22:46,360
但不是一个
But he's not...

1278
01:22:46,560 --> 01:22:48,280
引用他原话就是
and I'm quoting him, here,

1279
01:22:48,400 --> 01:22:50,600
"彻头彻尾的混蛋"
"100% a dick."

1280
01:22:51,020 --> 01:22:52,270
你信他吗
Do you believe him?

1281
01:22:52,720 --> 01:22:55,650
我也不知道有没有彻头彻尾的混蛋  夫人
I don't know that I believe anyone is 100% a dick, ma'am.

1282
01:22:55,880 --> 01:22:58,800
我是问  你相信他是来帮忙的吗
I mean, do you believe that he is here to help?

1283
01:23:02,520 --> 01:23:03,520
信啊
Yeah.

1284
01:23:13,600 --> 01:23:15,090
不明舰队逼近中
A fleet approaches.

1285
01:23:15,520 --> 01:23:17,120
看起来像是掠夺者
They appear to be Ravagers.

1286
01:23:28,390 --> 01:23:29,400
开火
Fire!

1287
01:23:40,640 --> 01:23:41,800
掩护就位
Cover it down.

1288
01:23:41,960 --> 01:23:43,880
全体下潜
Submerge!

1289
01:23:56,840 --> 01:23:58,380
火箭  快上
Rocket, hurry!

1290
01:24:04,560 --> 01:24:05,770
全体飞行员下潜
All pilots, dive!

1291
01:24:05,800 --> 01:24:07,080
他们在我们正下方
They're beneath us!

1292
01:24:15,920 --> 01:24:17,330
疏散全体市民
Evacuate the city.

1293
01:24:17,480 --> 01:24:20,960
我们的首要任务是确保人民安全撤离
Our priority is to get our people away from the battle.

1294
01:24:28,000 --> 01:24:29,790
全速推进  动作快
Forward thrust, now!

1295
01:24:42,520 --> 01:24:43,520
加把劲儿
Come on!

1296
01:24:45,240 --> 01:24:46,840
奎尔  勇度  趁现在
Quill! Yondu! Now!

1297
01:25:09,160 --> 01:25:10,650
妈的
Aw, hell!

1298
01:25:10,800 --> 01:25:12,280
我被击落了  奎尔
I'm going down, Quill!

1299
01:25:12,400 --> 01:25:14,160
别给我耍花招  小子
No more games with me, boy!

1300
01:25:14,420 --> 01:25:16,920
完事之后我们再会
I'll see you at the end of this!

1301
01:25:23,520 --> 01:25:25,300
他们人太多了  火箭
There are too many of them, Rocket!

1302
01:25:25,720 --> 01:25:27,440
我们没法突围
We'll never make it up there!

1303
01:25:42,480 --> 01:25:43,600
彼得·奎尔
Peter Quill.

1304
01:25:43,760 --> 01:25:46,160
我是新星军团的丹纳利安·萨尔
This is Denarian Saal of the Nova Corps.

1305
01:25:46,320 --> 01:25:49,600
先声明一下  我始终认为不该相信你
For the record, I advised against trusting you here.

1306
01:25:49,760 --> 01:25:51,120
看来我的"混蛋"消息他们收到了
They got my "Dick" Message!

1307
01:25:51,560 --> 01:25:52,720
用事实证明我错了吧
Prove me wrong.

1308
01:26:00,200 --> 01:26:02,080
爽
Yes!

1309
01:26:23,490 --> 01:26:24,650
够嗨
Yes!

1310
01:26:27,760 --> 01:26:29,560
我们和凯文·贝肯差不多厉害吧
We're just like Kevin Bacon.

1311
01:26:33,680 --> 01:26:35,410
右舷核心部位受创
The starboard kern has been breached!

1312
01:26:35,460 --> 01:26:36,740
他们闯进来了
We have been boarded.

1313
01:26:36,760 --> 01:26:38,170
继续向前推进
Continue our approach.

1314
01:26:38,320 --> 01:26:39,600
但是新星军团也掺合进来了
But the Nova Corps have engaged.

1315
01:26:39,760 --> 01:26:42,410
着陆之后一切就都不是问题了
None of that will matter once we reach the surface.

1316
01:26:42,520 --> 01:26:43,520
关闭所有安全门
Seal security doors!

1317
01:26:43,760 --> 01:26:44,850
赶紧
Now!

1318
01:26:46,520 --> 01:26:48,010
别挡老娘的路
Get out of my way!

1319
01:26:59,730 --> 01:27:01,610
老天
Oh, man.

1320
01:27:01,720 --> 01:27:03,360
所有新星飞行员听令
All Nova pilots,

1321
01:27:03,650 --> 01:27:06,200
全体对接形成封锁网
interlock and form a blockade.

1322
01:27:06,280 --> 01:27:10,120
务必阻止暗黑星号着陆
The Dark Aster must not reach the ground.

1323
01:27:22,640 --> 01:27:23,840
已锁入
Locked in!

1324
01:27:24,640 --> 01:27:25,840
已锁入
Locked in.

1325
01:27:27,400 --> 01:27:28,400
已锁入
We're locked in.

1326
01:28:06,680 --> 01:28:08,880
我什么都看不见
I can barely see.

1327
01:28:35,240 --> 01:28:36,960
你什么时候学了这一招
When did you learn to do that?

1328
01:28:37,520 --> 01:28:38,600
我猜答案肯定是
Pretty sure the answer is

1329
01:28:38,760 --> 01:28:40,360
"我是格鲁特"
"I am Groot."

1330
01:28:41,520 --> 01:28:44,040
飞行甲板就在前方300米处
The flight deck is 300 meters this way.

1331
01:28:46,800 --> 01:28:47,920
我希望你们知道
I want you all to know that

1332
01:28:47,950 --> 01:28:49,690
感谢你们  不在意我的鲁莽之举
I am grateful for your acceptance

1333
01:28:49,690 --> 01:28:50,730
依然接受我
after my blunders.

1334
01:28:51,200 --> 01:28:53,400
再次有朋友相伴的感觉...
It is pleasing to once again have...

1335
01:28:54,040 --> 01:28:55,040
真棒
friends.

1336
01:28:56,120 --> 01:28:59,050
奎尔  你是我朋友
You, Quill, are my friend.

1337
01:28:59,080 --> 01:29:00,280
谢了
Thanks.

1338
01:29:00,480 --> 01:29:03,210
这颗蠢树也是我朋友
This dumb tree, he is my friend.

1339
01:29:04,720 --> 01:29:05,920
还有这个绿婊子也
And this green whore, she, too...

1340
01:29:06,040 --> 01:29:07,560
给我闭嘴
You must stop!

1341
01:29:10,440 --> 01:29:13,200
卡魔拉  看看你干的好事
Gamora, look at what you have done.

1342
01:29:13,920 --> 01:29:15,880
你还是一如既往的软弱
You have always been weak.

1343
01:29:16,160 --> 01:29:18,280
愚蠢  背信弃...
You stupid, traitorous...

1344
01:29:23,440 --> 01:29:25,760
不要这么跟我朋友说话
Nobody talks to my friends like that.

1345
01:29:26,920 --> 01:29:28,000
你们去飞行甲板
Head to the flight deck.

1346
01:29:28,160 --> 01:29:30,810
我去切断安全门的动力
I'll shut down the power to the security doors.

1347
01:29:38,060 --> 01:29:40,600
勇度·尤冬塔
Yondu Udonta.

1348
01:29:40,760 --> 01:29:44,810
命令自己的手下向新星军团投降
Order your men to turn on the Nova Corps.

1349
01:30:01,040 --> 01:30:02,560
玩够了没  掠夺者
Enough nonsense, Ravager!

1350
01:30:02,720 --> 01:30:04,520
你的死期到...
Time to die...

1351
01:30:37,240 --> 01:30:38,870
星云  别这样
Nebula, please.

1352
01:30:52,840 --> 01:30:55,460
够了  死灵舰队飞行员
Enough of this. Necrocraft pilots,

1353
01:30:55,720 --> 01:30:58,010
开始自我献祭吧
enact immolation initiative.

1354
01:31:01,280 --> 01:31:02,850
他们冲下去轰炸城市了
They're dive-bombing the city!

1355
01:31:02,880 --> 01:31:04,680
丹纳利安·萨尔  需要解除连锁吗
Denarian Saal, should we break formation?

1356
01:31:04,840 --> 01:31:06,490
不行  保持阵形
No! Hold your positions.

1357
01:31:38,120 --> 01:31:39,510
拖住罗南  萨尔
Keep Ronan up there, Saal.

1358
01:31:39,540 --> 01:31:41,370
下面市民的安全交给我们了
We'll take care of the people down here.

1359
01:31:41,400 --> 01:31:43,600
我居然要听命于一只小仓鼠
I can't believe I'm taking orders from a hamster.

1360
01:31:46,800 --> 01:31:48,350
星爵
Star-Lord.

1361
01:31:48,520 --> 01:31:49,690
终于记住了
Finally.

1362
01:32:00,440 --> 01:32:01,480
你个卑鄙的贼
You thief!

1363
01:32:13,100 --> 01:32:16,200
你们休想攻到罗南那儿去
You will never make it to Ronan.

1364
01:32:21,760 --> 01:32:24,200
在死灵舰着陆之前就把他们轰下来
Everybody shoot them before they hit the ground.

1365
01:32:32,840 --> 01:32:34,200
来吧
Come on!

1366
01:33:17,040 --> 01:33:20,520
手指划过喉咙就是杀人
Finger to the throat means death.

1367
01:33:26,360 --> 01:33:27,770
我用比喻了
Metaphor.

1368
01:33:27,920 --> 01:33:29,200
差不多吧
Yeah, sorta.

1369
01:33:29,700 --> 01:33:30,520
不是吧
Oh, no.

1370
01:33:58,520 --> 01:33:59,930
山达尔
Xandar!

1371
01:34:00,210 --> 01:34:03,250
接受制裁吧
You stand accused.

1372
01:34:04,040 --> 01:34:08,370
可悲的和平条约也救不了你们了
Your wretched peace treaty will not save you now.

1373
01:34:08,880 --> 01:34:12,580
跟条约一起葬身火海吧
It is the tinder on which you burn.

1374
01:34:36,940 --> 01:34:37,760
火箭
Rocket!

1375
01:34:37,920 --> 01:34:39,720
坚持住  萨尔  再坚...
Hold on, Saal, just...

1376
01:35:06,300 --> 01:35:07,680
奎尔  你得快点了
Quill, you gotta hurry.

1377
01:35:07,840 --> 01:35:09,530
市民倒是都被疏散了
The city's been evacuated,

1378
01:35:09,560 --> 01:35:11,890
可我们还在苦战呢
but we're getting our asses kicked down here.

1379
01:35:12,000 --> 01:35:13,680
卡魔拉还没把门打开
Gamora hasn't opened the door!

1380
01:35:38,750 --> 01:35:39,960
星云
Nebula!

1381
01:35:40,900 --> 01:35:43,800
妹妹  帮我们一起打败罗南吧
Sister, help us fight Ronan.

1382
01:35:43,840 --> 01:35:45,460
你很清楚他就是个疯子
You know he's crazy.

1383
01:35:45,600 --> 01:35:47,470
你们俩都是疯子
I know you're both crazy.

1384
01:35:47,840 --> 01:35:49,000
不
No!

1385
01:35:51,640 --> 01:35:52,300
什么鬼...
What the...?

1386
01:35:54,000 --> 01:35:54,890
滚出去
Get out!

1387
01:36:37,180 --> 01:36:38,390
你成功了
You did it!

1388
01:37:04,260 --> 01:37:05,970
之前我错了
I was mistaken.

1389
01:37:06,000 --> 01:37:08,090
我确实记得你家人
I do remember your family.

1390
01:37:08,240 --> 01:37:09,960
她们临死时的叫声
Their screams were

1391
01:37:10,120 --> 01:37:12,240
那么可悲  我
pitiful. I...

1392
01:39:09,360 --> 01:39:10,480
不  格鲁特
No, Groot!

1393
01:39:10,830 --> 01:39:12,250
别这样
You can't.

1394
01:39:12,280 --> 01:39:13,770
你会死的
You'll die.

1395
01:39:14,320 --> 01:39:16,160
为什么要这么做
Why are you doing this?

1396
01:39:16,510 --> 01:39:17,430
为什么
Why?

1397
01:39:24,400 --> 01:39:26,180
我们
We...

1398
01:39:26,360 --> 01:39:27,600
是
are...

1399
01:39:28,040 --> 01:39:30,190
格鲁特
Groot.

1400
01:40:33,960 --> 01:40:36,000
真是个白痴
I called him an idiot.

1401
01:40:58,720 --> 01:41:00,640
是你杀了格鲁特
You killed Groot!

1402
01:41:04,450 --> 01:41:06,130
看吧
Behold!

1403
01:41:07,000 --> 01:41:10,330
看这支银河护卫队
Your guardians of the galaxy.

1404
01:41:10,620 --> 01:41:12,960
你们护卫了什么
What fruit have they wrought?

1405
01:41:13,120 --> 01:41:17,290
现在我终于得偿所愿
Only that my father and his father

1406
01:41:17,320 --> 01:41:20,880
为我父亲和爷爷报了仇
shall finally know vengeance.

1407
01:41:21,040 --> 01:41:23,280
山达尔的子民
People of Xandar,

1408
01:41:23,720 --> 01:41:27,260
背弃你们卑微的信仰
the time has come to rejoice

1409
01:41:27,300 --> 01:41:31,300
迎接我的时刻到了
and renounce your paltry gods!

1410
01:41:31,840 --> 01:41:35,440
你们即将得到救赎
Your salvation is at hand.

1411
01:41:47,820 --> 01:41:49,200
听这几句
Listen to these words.

1412
01:41:58,420 --> 01:42:00,050
用力舞起来
Now bring it down hard!

1413
01:42:03,600 --> 01:42:04,680
你在干嘛
What are you doing?

1414
01:42:05,200 --> 01:42:07,770
比舞啊  老兄  就我们俩
Dance-off, Bro. Me and you.

1415
01:42:11,310 --> 01:42:12,060
卡魔拉
Gamora.

1416
01:42:13,640 --> 01:42:15,190
委婉拒绝  收回邀请
Subtle. Take it back.

1417
01:42:16,120 --> 01:42:18,360
你到底在搞什么鬼
What are you doing?

1418
01:42:18,680 --> 01:42:21,050
分你的心啊  大蠢蛋
I'm distracting you, you big turd blossom.

1419
01:42:37,240 --> 01:42:38,730
不
No!

1420
01:43:12,720 --> 01:43:17,000
彼得  握住我的手
Peter! Take my hand!

1421
01:43:21,130 --> 01:43:23,210
握住我的手  彼得
Take my hand, Peter.

1422
01:43:24,200 --> 01:43:25,300
妈妈
Mom.

1423
01:43:26,060 --> 01:43:28,640
握住我的手
Take my hand!

1424
01:44:22,480 --> 01:44:23,940
你们只是凡人
You're mortal!

1425
01:44:24,720 --> 01:44:25,900
怎么可能
How?

1426
01:44:26,100 --> 01:44:28,450
你不是说过吗  婊子
You said it yourself, bitch.

1427
01:44:28,480 --> 01:44:30,890
我们可是银河护卫队
We're the Guardians of the Galaxy.

1428
01:45:00,520 --> 01:45:02,190
不错  不错
Well, well, well.

1429
01:45:02,380 --> 01:45:04,480
好一场光影盛宴
Quite the light show.

1430
01:45:05,840 --> 01:45:07,900
大团圆结局啊
Ain't this sweet.

1431
01:45:09,040 --> 01:45:11,320
不过在你们嘿咻嘿咻之前
But you got some business to attend to

1432
01:45:11,420 --> 01:45:14,160
先给我把正事办了
before all the nookie-nookie starts.

1433
01:45:15,840 --> 01:45:18,040
彼得  你不能给他
Peter, you can't. Peter.

1434
01:45:18,200 --> 01:45:20,240
你得三思  勇度
You gotta reconsider this, Yondu.

1435
01:45:20,720 --> 01:45:22,210
我不知道你要把它卖给谁
I don't know who you're selling this to,

1436
01:45:22,250 --> 01:45:24,250
不过能让宇宙安定平稳的唯一方法
but the only way the universe can survive

1437
01:45:24,280 --> 01:45:26,670
就是把它交给新星军团保管
is if you give it to the Nova Corps.

1438
01:45:27,000 --> 01:45:29,760
都说我长得像菩萨
I may be as pretty as an angel,

1439
01:45:31,400 --> 01:45:33,760
可我没有菩萨心肠
but I sure as hell ain't one.

1440
01:45:35,000 --> 01:45:36,680
快交给我吧  孩子
Hand it over, son.

1441
01:45:53,360 --> 01:45:54,360
勇度
Yondu.

1442
01:45:57,440 --> 01:46:01,330
决不能打开宇宙灵球  你知道的吧
Do not open that Orb. You know that, right?

1443
01:46:01,360 --> 01:46:03,800
你也看见它的威力了
You've seen what it does to people.

1444
01:46:14,560 --> 01:46:16,800
奎尔这小子还挺懂事
Yeah, Quill turned out okay.

1445
01:46:17,680 --> 01:46:19,930
当初没有按他爹的要求把他送过去
It's probably good we didn't deliver him to his dad

1446
01:46:19,980 --> 01:46:21,400
也许是个正确的决定
like we was hired to do.

1447
01:46:21,520 --> 01:46:24,250
是啊  他爹就是个混球
Yeah, that guy was a jackass.

1448
01:46:29,120 --> 01:46:31,110
等他发现宇宙灵球被我掉包了
He is gonna be so pissed when he realizes

1449
01:46:31,140 --> 01:46:32,730
非气炸不可
I switched out the Orb on him.

1450
01:46:35,440 --> 01:46:37,530
他一定会砍死你  彼得
He was gonna kill you, Peter.

1451
01:46:38,480 --> 01:46:40,160
是啊
Oh, I know.

1452
01:46:42,040 --> 01:46:44,460
不过他也算是我唯一的亲人了
But he was about the only family I had.

1453
01:46:46,560 --> 01:46:47,600
不
No.

1454
01:46:48,880 --> 01:46:50,080
不止是他
He wasn't.

1455
01:47:38,320 --> 01:47:39,890
你们怎么连这个都知道
Why would you even know this?

1456
01:47:40,000 --> 01:47:40,900
当初抓你回来后
When we arrested you,

1457
01:47:40,900 --> 01:47:42,810
我们发现你的神经系统有些异常
we noticed an anomaly in your nervous system,

1458
01:47:42,840 --> 01:47:44,520
于是帮你做了检查
so we had it checked out.

1459
01:47:45,560 --> 01:47:47,230
所以我不是地星人
I'm not Terran?

1460
01:47:47,320 --> 01:47:48,840
有一半血统来自地星
You are half Terran.

1461
01:47:49,000 --> 01:47:52,640
你母亲是地球人  至于你父亲
Your mother was of Earth. Your father, well,

1462
01:47:52,800 --> 01:47:56,360
他是某种我们从未接触过的远古生灵
he's something very ancient we've never seen here before.

1463
01:47:56,680 --> 01:47:57,400
怪不得
That could be why

1464
01:47:57,430 --> 01:48:00,240
你握着宝石那么久却没事
you were able to hold the Stone for as long as you did.

1465
01:48:01,370 --> 01:48:03,200
你的朋友们来齐了
Your friends have arrived.

1466
01:48:04,160 --> 01:48:06,080
我谨代表新星军团
On behalf of the Nova Corps,

1467
01:48:06,790 --> 01:48:10,040
向你们致以最真诚的谢意
we'd like to express our profound gratitude

1468
01:48:10,250 --> 01:48:12,880
谢谢你们拯救了山达尔
for your help in saving Xandar.

1469
01:48:13,680 --> 01:48:16,510
你们可以跟随丹纳利安·戴
If you will follow Denarian Dey,

1470
01:48:16,560 --> 01:48:18,160
他有东西要带你们看
he has something to show you.

1471
01:48:18,320 --> 01:48:19,630
谢谢了  新星至尊
Thank you, Nova Prime.

1472
01:48:28,680 --> 01:48:31,060
你帮妻女报了仇
Your wife and child shall rest well

1473
01:48:31,560 --> 01:48:33,400
现在她们能安息了
knowing that you have avenged them.

1474
01:48:33,680 --> 01:48:34,840
是啊
Yes.

1475
01:48:35,000 --> 01:48:36,920
不过说到底罗南只是个傀儡
Of course, Ronan was only a puppet.

1476
01:48:37,680 --> 01:48:40,200
得杀掉灭霸才算报仇
It's really Thanos I need to kill.

1477
01:48:42,520 --> 01:48:45,280
我们想保留它原本的样子
We tried to keep it as close to the original as possible.

1478
01:48:45,880 --> 01:48:47,840
已经尽全力做了相关修复了
We salvaged as much as we could.

1479
01:48:50,960 --> 01:48:51,960
我
I...

1480
01:48:53,960 --> 01:48:55,080
多谢了
Thank you.

1481
01:48:56,710 --> 01:48:58,210
我也有妻儿
I have a family.

1482
01:48:58,800 --> 01:49:00,630
多亏你她们才能活下来
They're alive because of you.

1483
01:49:04,550 --> 01:49:07,350
你们的犯罪记录已经被抹掉了
Your criminal records have also been expunged.

1484
01:49:07,480 --> 01:49:08,520
不过还是得提醒你们
However, I have to warn

1485
01:49:08,550 --> 01:49:11,480
遵纪守法才是好公民
you against breaking any laws in the future.

1486
01:49:12,080 --> 01:49:12,730
问一下
Question.

